COMMENT     VALIDATED REFSEQ: This record has undergone validation or
            preliminary review. The reference sequence was derived from
            AK161446.1, BC079615.1, BF730624.1 and BE952624.1.
            
            On Sep 21, 2012 this sequence version replaced NM_023472.1.
            
            Transcript Variant: This variant (4) differs in the 3' UTR and has
            an alternate splice site in the 3' coding region, which results in
            a frameshift, compared to variant 1. The encoded isoform (d) is
            longer and has a distinct C-terminus, compared to isoform a.
            
